282
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:12,900
A stronger self, of course.

283
00:26:15,460 --> 00:26:17,220
A stronger self?

284
00:26:17,220 --> 00:26:18,690
Yes.

285
00:26:20,430 --> 00:26:26,510
All these years, raising Meng Meng alone, I had faced many hardships.

286
00:26:27,390 --> 00:26:30,810
I had neither support nor a way out.

287
00:26:30,810 --> 00:26:33,520
