290
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:43,610
My reputation also became bad,

291
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:46,900
but I gained skills as well as courage.

292
00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:51,230
Things that belong to me, no one can take these assets away from me.

293
00:26:55,030 --> 00:26:57,150
Yes.

294
00:26:57,150 --> 00:27:03,310
Before getting a divorce, I never would've thought I could be a saleswoman.

295
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:08,230
After divorcing, I have become one of the backbones of the sales department.

296
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:10,750
Speaking of that,

297
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:14,540
Director Yuan, a toast to you. Thank you for taking me in.

298
00:27:14,540 --> 00:27:16,340
