328
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:15,180
It just flopped.

329
00:29:15,180 --> 00:29:18,040
Oh, right, Older Sister!  If you want anything, you can take it.

330
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:22,760
However,...I think the best thing for you to take is me.

331
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:24,990
Out of everything here, you are worth the least.

332
00:29:24,990 --> 00:29:27,620
Why are you so bad at recognizing product value?

333
00:29:27,620 --> 00:29:29,260
