340
00:29:50,790 --> 00:29:55,100
This... I think this one still has ¥30.

341
00:29:55,100 --> 00:29:57,830
This has been frozen.

342
00:29:57,830 --> 00:30:00,030
This is useless, too.

343
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:05,320
Oh right, on Wechat, I-I-I still have 30 something yuan.

344
00:30:06,390 --> 00:30:09,140
Wh-Why so little?

345
00:30:09,140 --> 00:30:12,640
I've always been poor, it's not like you don't know.

346
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:14,300
What about your car?

347
00:30:14,300 --> 00:30:15,460
I mortgaged it to my friend.

348
00:30:15,460 --> 00:30:18,470
